WEBVTT

00:00:08.722 --> 00:00:13.253
Australians call them “runners." 
The British know them as “trainers."

00:00:13.253 --> 00:00:17.323
Americans refer to them as “tennis shoes” 
or “sneakers."

00:00:17.323 --> 00:00:20.871
Whatever you call them, 
these rubber-soled, casual shoes

00:00:20.871 --> 00:00:24.280
are worn by billions of people 
around the world.

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:27.320
Originally invented 
in the late 19th century,

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:31.109
these simple canvas and rubber creations 
have changed a lot